# Building the site

When you need to run the Seed Nuggets build, use:

```bash
just build
```

Do **not** run `python3 src/build.py` (or `python src/build.py`) directly. That uses the system Python and fails with "Markdown pages require the markdown package." The justfile runs the build with `.venv/bin/python`, which has dependencies installed. 